TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.QUARTER, A.COMP_MONTH, A.COMP_YEAR, B.COMP_PERIOD, A.PAYEE_DISTRICT_UNIT, A.PAYEE_CURRENT_UNIT, A.PAYEE_CODE, A.PAYEE_NAME, A.AGENCY_NAME, A.PAYEE_CURRENT_CLASS_CODE, A.PAYEE_RANK, A.CONTRACT_DATE, A.CONTRACT_QUARTER, A.TERMINATIONDATE, A.PONUMBER, A.POLICY_SUBMISSION_DATE, A.RISK_COMMENCEMENT_DATE, A.POLICY_INCEPTION_DATE, A.COMPENSATIONDATE, A.CASE_COUNT, A.FYC, A.AI_PAID, A.AI_CLAWBACK, A.AI_PAYMENT, 'AI' as EVENTTYPEID, A.COMPONENT_CODE as COMPONENT_CODE FROM ai_monthly_report A, (select to_date(TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'yyyy-mm-dd') as comp_period from in_etl_control where TXT_KEY_STRING='OPER_CYCLE_DATE') B where A.quarter in (select name as quarter from cs_period where calendarseq = 2251799813685250 and periodtypeseq = 2814749767106563 --and name='Q1 2017' and enddate-1 = (select to_date(TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'yyyy-mm-dd') from in_etl_control where TXT_KEY_STRING='OPER_CYCLE_DATE')) and A.ai_payment is not null

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CS_EVENTTYPE.EVENTTYPEID as EVENTTYPEID FROM CS_EVENTTYPE WHERE CS_EVENTTYPE.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE('22000101','YYYYMMDD')
